videos.headline: Georgia strikes first with 5-yd TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Riley Ridley for a 5-yard Bulldogs touchdown.

videos.headline: Swift pushes into end zone
videos.description: De'Andre Swift keeps Georgia's offense rolling with a 1-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech answers with 100-yard kickoff return TD
videos.description: Juanyeh Thomas returns a kickoff 100 yards, his second straight game with a kickoff return touchdown.

videos.headline: Holloman stretches for TD catch
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Jeremiah Holloman to give Georgia a 21-7 lead over Georgia Tech.

videos.headline: Fromm keeps Bulldogs rolling with 44-yd TD pass
videos.description: Jake Fromm goes deep and connects with Mecole Hardman for a 44-yard Georgia touchdown, opening up its lead over Georgia Tech.

videos.headline: Holyfield punches in touchdown
videos.description: Elijah Holyfield leaps over Georgia Tech's line and stretches the ball into the end zone for an 8-yard Georgia touchdown.

videos.headline: Fromm throws 4th passing TD vs. Georgia Tech
videos.description: Jake Fromm connects with Riley Ridley for the duo's second touchdown collaboration on the day.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech picks up first offensive TD of game
videos.description: Qua Searcy squeezes into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown for Georgia Tech.

videos.headline: Fromm throws 4 TDs in Georgia's rout of Georgia Tech
videos.description: Jake Fromm's arm was on display as he threw four touchdowns to help Georgia beat Georgia Tech 45-21 and improve to 11-1.
